name: Jazzy Snake
description:
Snake, without Stakes.

This is Snake, but you cannot eat yourself, there is no boundry, and you can eat as much as you want.  The food will never run out.

Just play.

Use Arrow keys to move.  Press S to take a screenshot.

Music from https://filmmusic.io
"Round Drums" by Kevin MacLeod (https://incompetech.com)
